Lixus For DevOps Command

=========== System Level Commands ==========
uname   # name of the operating system
uptime  # how long system is running 
who     
whoami
which   ----- which bash  ----which cp  -- show the location of the file 
id      -- it show the user id or check other users id or what group of this user is member of 
sudo
passwd   -- show the list of user from . like /ect/passwd
shutdown   --- sudo shutdown --- 
reboot
apt
yum
dnf
pacman
portage
